<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这真荒唐。”唐僧说，“为什么要抓我们呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>官府的人把师徒四人又带回了村子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们昨晚抢劫了寇员外的家。”一个人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”八戒喊道，“我们从来没抢劫过谁的家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特别是寇员外。他对我们很好！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“被偷的东西都在你们这里。”那人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们还有从马厩里偷的两匹马。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那都是从真强盗那里拿来的。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们正要把所有东西都还给寇员外！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个人笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢？你们从真强盗们那里拿到了所有的东西？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那你说，现在真强盗们在哪儿？嗯？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空叹了口气。“我把他们都放走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个人又笑了。“哦，你可真好啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空知道那个官府的人不相信自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他们到了村子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多人都想来看热闹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>官府的人把师徒四人带进了官府。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>官府大人看到唐僧他们，皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把他们关起来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是误会。”唐僧哀求道，“我们不能进大牢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要去西天佛祖那里取经，这非常重要。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>官府大人摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“佛祖不会让杀人犯进入西天的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杀人犯？”悟净说，“你在说什么啊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们杀了寇员外。”官府大人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧的脸色苍白。“寇员外死了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>官府大人朝唐僧眯起眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，寇夫人看见你们杀了他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人被推进了大牢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门哐地被关上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧哭了起来。“这太可怕了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒握紧了拳头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个寇夫人陷害了我们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。”悟净点头说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，她为什么那么做呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今晚我去打听打听。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，悟空。”唐僧露出了感激的表情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得证明自己的清白！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，悟空变成蜜蜂飞出大牢，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>朝寇员外家里飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到寇夫人正趴在一副棺材上，伤心地痛哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空变回原来的样子藏在窗帘后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他模仿寇员外的声音说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“夫人！是我，你丈夫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇夫人睁大了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“丈夫？真的是你吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么跟官府大人说是唐僧和他的徒弟们杀了我？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇夫人犹豫了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我……我很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你希望他们呆在这里，他们却非要走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是对我们的一种侮辱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这样做太不好！”悟空喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>房子的墙晃了一下，寇夫人吓得抱住了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空继续说：“明天你得去跟官府大人说唐僧他们是清白的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不然，我会一辈子跟着你，折磨你的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>眼泪从那女人的眼睛里涌出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明天我就跟官府大人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我答应你。你千万不要跟着我，折磨我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又飞回官府。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看见官府大人正坐在桌边看什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空飞到房顶上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他变成了一只巨大的妖怪，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>并把一只脚伸到了下面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>官府大人看见那只大脚，吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他手里的东西掉了下来</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空开始说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是游魂，是佛祖派我来的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇夫人对你说了谎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧没有杀死寇员外。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧要去西天取经，这件事很重要。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你不放了他和他的徒弟们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我就把另一只脚也伸下来</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>339473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，我要踩平这个村子，什么也不留！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>